## 1. System Architecture

The system follows a modular 5-layer architecture designed for maintainability and computational efficiency.

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph DATA_SOURCES [Data Sources Layer]
        BD[Base Data 2026]
        OF[OFWW Schedule]
        FG[Daily Fuel Gas Composition]
    end

    subgraph UTILITY [Utility Functions Layer]
        I1[fnInterp1D]
        I2[fnInterp2D]
        IF[fnInterpFuelCurve]
        RH[fnRH_at_Comp_Inlet]
    end

    subgraph CF_FUNCTIONS [Correction Factor Layer]
        C1[fnCF_CIT]
        C2[fnCF_RH]
        C3[fnCF_ShaftSpeed]
        C4[fnCF_FuelTemp]
        C5[fnCF_InletDP]
        C6[fnCF_ExhaustPressure]
        C7[fnCF_ExhaustDP]
        C8[fnCF_BaroPressure]
        C9[fnCF_FuelComp]
    end

    subgraph PERFORMANCE [Performance Calculation Layer]
        GA[GT1A Performance]
        GB[GT1B Performance]
        GC[GT1C Performance]
    end

    subgraph REPORTING [Reporting Layer]
        CS[GT Combined Summary]
    end

    BD --> GA
    BD --> GB
    BD --> GC
    OF --> BD
    FG --> GA
    FG --> GB
    FG --> GC

    I1 --> C1
    I1 --> C4
    I1 --> C7
    I1 --> IF
    IF --> C9
    I1 --> C9
    I2 --> C2
    I2 --> C3
    I2 --> C5
    I2 --> C6
    I2 --> C8
    RH --> GA
    RH --> GB
    RH --> GC

    C1 & C2 & C3 & C4 & C5 & C6 & C7 & C8 & C9 --> GA
    C1 & C2 & C3 & C4 & C5 & C6 & C7 & C8 & C9 --> GB
    C1 & C2 & C3 & C4 & C5 & C6 & C7 & C8 & C9 --> GC

    GA --> CS
    GB --> CS
    GC --> CS
```

